item.title: By: Gregg Eldred
item.dc:creator: Gregg Eldred
item.description: <p>This is one of those movies that I will watch whenever and wherever it is on cable. I really ought to buy it. And the reason I watched it in the first place? John Cusack - I think he is an underappreciated actor. Excellent movie.</p>
item.content:encoded: This is one of those movies that I will watch whenever and wherever it is on cable. I really ought to buy it. And the reason I watched it in the first place? John Cusack – I think he is an underappreciated actor. Excellent movie.
